MASTER-OAGH robotic telescope  (Global MASTER-Net: http://observ.pereplet.ru, Lipunov et al., 2010, Advances in Astronomy, vol. 2010, 30L)  located in Mexico (OAGH National Institute for Astrophysics, Optics and Electronics) was pointed to the Swift GRB 220412B ( J.D. Gropp et al., GCN 31886) errorbox  61446 sec after notice time and 61475 sec after trigger time at 2022-04-13 10:11:24 UT, with upper limit up to  17.5 mag. The observations began at zenith distance = 77 deg. The sun  altitude  is -32.6 deg. 

The galactic latitude b = -34 deg., longitude l = 53 deg.


Real time updated cover map and OT discovered available here: 
https://master.sai.msu.ru/site/master2/observ.php?id=1940975

